---
---

<section id="proces" class="py-28 bg-[#080808] relative border-y border-white/5">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-20">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-indigo-400 mb-4">
        <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-indigo-500"></span>
        <span>04. Prosty Proces</span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-4xl sm:text-6xl font-black uppercase italic tracking-tighter text-white leading-none">
        Od pomysłu do klientów. <br />
        <span class="text-white/40">W trzech prostych krokach.</span>
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <!-- Step 1 -->
      <div class="p-8 rounded-[2.5rem] bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/5 relative group hover:border-indigo-500/30 transition-all">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-8">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10 flex items-center justify-center font-black text-indigo-400 text-lg">
            01
          </div>
          <span class="text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-white/30">Krok 1</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-black uppercase italic tracking-tight text-white mb-4">
          Wycena & Brief
        </h3>
        <p class="text-xs text-white/50 leading-relaxed font-medium">
          Wypełniasz krótki kalkulator online. Określasz swoją branżę i cele – zajmuje to mniej niż 2 minuty.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 2 -->
      <div class="p-8 rounded-[2.5rem] bg-gradient-to-b from-indigo-950/30 to-black border border-indigo-500/30 relative group hover:border-indigo-500/60 transition-all shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(99,102,241,0.1)]">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-8">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-indigo-500 text-white flex items-center justify-center font-black text-lg shadow-lg shadow-indigo-500/30">
            02
          </div>
          <span class="text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-indigo-400 font-bold">W 48 Godzin</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-black uppercase italic tracking-tight text-white mb-4">
          Projektowanie
        </h3>
        <p class="text-xs text-indigo-200/70 leading-relaxed font-medium">
          W 48 godzin przygotowujemy gotową stronę z tekstami i grafiką. Przesyłamy Ci aktywny podgląd do akceptacji.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Step 3 -->
      <div class="p-8 rounded-[2.5rem] bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/5 relative group hover:border-indigo-500/30 transition-all">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-8">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10 flex items-center justify-center font-black text-indigo-400 text-lg">
            03
          </div>
          <span class="text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-white/30">Krok 3</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-black uppercase italic tracking-tight text-white mb-4">
          Publikacja & Reklamy
        </h3>
        <p class="text-xs text-white/50 leading-relaxed font-medium">
          Podpinamy domenę i włączamy pozycjonowanie w Google oraz kampanie płatne. Zaczynasz odbierać telefony od klientów.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
